  <h1>UC Libraries Space Utilization Dashboard</h1>
  <p class="muted">A Power BI dashboard combining gate counts, room reservations, and reference activity to surface usage trends and support space optimization decisions.</p>

  <h2>What I built</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Data integration from multiple operational sources</li>
    <li>KPI design for utilization and trend monitoring</li>
    <li>Interactive dashboard views for stakeholders (filters, drillthrough patterns)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Impact</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Supported space optimization planning with clearer utilization insight</li>
    <li>Reduced manual reporting and improved visibility into room usage patterns</li>
  </ul>

